<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi <%= @user.email %></h1>
    <p>
      You, or someone using this email, recently registered for Easyauth. Welcome! All that's left now is to validate your account.<br />
      On the registration page, where it's asking for a validation code, please enter: <em><%= @code %></em>. Then you're all set!<br />
      If you did not request this email, please disregard it; your information will be purged from our database in approximately 24 hours.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
